{
  "stem": "14737.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Don't come back to Hungary, they write us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They are sending messages, don't come back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Stay there as long as you can.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because in Hungary, you cannot achieve nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They are already there from before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At one point, there's a story that those students who want-- not students-- who wants to go to the [INAUDIBLE], who wants to emigrate to Israel there's a place they call it [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know whether you have-- even know what it means, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a place, if you are a Zionist, and you are going to work for two, three years at a certain place, you'll be able to get a certificate.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the Germans did the following.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They needed some work there, and farm [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They said-- they allowed a Jewish organization under the name of [INAUDIBLE] to open a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They didn't need it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some farmers, big one or small one, they needed workers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the Germans said, we'll have workers here from students or from others.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And what are we going to do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We allow [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They have never meant to have it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so I wrote [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And went there and worked there a few days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I realized that it's only a phase.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "No one will go [? after ?] Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I left it, and came back to Brno again, and started concentrating what to do next.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I had a passport, which was valid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I figured maybe I'll be able to go still to France.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But there is now a story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You need an exit visa.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's not that you have a passport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Passport doesn't mean nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "With a passport, you just-- you need from the Germans an allowance, regardless who you are.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
